name: Skybyrinth
description:
The rules are simple:

  • Collect the yellow 'power of 2's'.
  • Avoid the timer to run out, this works as a total score multiplier at the end of each maze.

When downloading this game you can choose to pay-what-you-want or just download it for free. 

System requirements:

At least 2gb Vram and 6gb ram.
